Notes: 1) This list was created using public/free subtitles, particularly from opensubtitles.org.
The order is based on the number of occurences of each word in the subtitles.
2) The English translation is by Google and can be un-reliable for some words.
3) You can change the translation from English to another language.
To do this you will first need to make a copy of this spreadsheet.  (File > Make a copy...)
Then replace the "en" in the function in the cells in Column C with your desired language code.
